By the end of this course, students will be able to:
1. describe how different sorts of individual differences may impact upon learning;
2. explain the major factors that affect human motivation;
3. devise classroom strategies to have a “feel” for individual differences in cognitive strategies and motivation among students;
4. design effective motivation-fostering strategies based on your knowledge of (b), and (c) above.

學生修畢本科後，能夠:
1. 描繪不同種類的個別差異對學習的影響；
2. 解釋影響人類學習動機的主因；
3. 於設計課教學策略去了解學生認知與動機上的個別差異；
4. 根據(b)及(c)的知識，設計一個有效孕育學習動機的方案。

